{
  "2202430": {
    "name": "航海日记2",
    "steam_appid": 2202430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/27525f037be39f218cf9eb88ec2fbfd4.avif?t=1728732179\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《航海日记2》中，你将化身来自中国的航海家，与来自全世界的玩家一起，从飘着煎饼果子香味的天津卫出发，率领舰队驶向未知的海域，这注定是一场充满机遇的旅程，通过积极的开辟商路，积累财富，你终将建立起属于你的海上帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/f06e934c5d68742b707d4139e1af889e.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/f06e934c5d68742b707d4139e1af889e.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/f06e934c5d68742b707d4139e1af889e.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这也注定是一场充满危险的旅程，你必须用利刃与大炮战胜那些穷凶极恶的海盗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/4378d3a244c8db91430dc4386a7344f9.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/4378d3a244c8db91430dc4386a7344f9.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/4378d3a244c8db91430dc4386a7344f9.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/84837e9a6ef02b612981582eb19b03b4.avif?t=1728732179\" width=615 height=100 /></span>每艘舰船都支持深度改造，从船尾、辅助帆、船首、船头、装甲到货仓，均可以根据需要安排，想打仗就多加大炮，想赚钱就多加货仓，想帅气就多加皮肤（狗头）~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/9ef07c57df01d642ee2e4305582e83ab.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/9ef07c57df01d642ee2e4305582e83ab.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/9ef07c57df01d642ee2e4305582e83ab.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时冒险中玩家也会结识来自世界各地的有趣角色，一起经历一段段精彩的冒险，你不仅能借此了解到他们背后的故事，还有机会将其招募入伙，组成一支能力独特又充满个性的冒险团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2fcaee9a7b6e9cf87a6c2e5a693a87cd.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2fcaee9a7b6e9cf87a6c2e5a693a87cd.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2fcaee9a7b6e9cf87a6c2e5a693a87cd.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而所有这些伙伴，都将在你的船上担负起相应的工作，根据他们的特长合理安排，才能达到最佳战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/24c36c30f429f2209f08314e59625ae0.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/24c36c30f429f2209f08314e59625ae0.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/24c36c30f429f2209f08314e59625ae0.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后玩家作为船长，将拥有十分丰富的职业与技能选择，同时获得更多强力装备、角色乃至战舰，让舰队实力不断提升，以挑战那些掩藏在深海当中的强敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/65959ee792c04c19e3098f3550e19792.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/65959ee792c04c19e3098f3550e19792.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/65959ee792c04c19e3098f3550e19792.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/4b819b99a9ab2c9fd7f25c84786dc1e8.avif?t=1728732179\" width=615 height=100 /></span>《航海日记2》中有着紧张激烈的即时海战，面对海盗，玩家必须率领舰队灵活“走位”，躲过一次次致命威胁，并通过合理的释放“技能”战胜强敌，别看这是海战，完全能打出moba式的爽快连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a30e4a4296843d44fdad7a51d089853d.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a30e4a4296843d44fdad7a51d089853d.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a30e4a4296843d44fdad7a51d089853d.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着冒险深入，玩家还将率领舰队进入一个个海上副本，面对那些更为强大也更加特别的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/7758f1f6acba35288bfcb743ad114d7e.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/7758f1f6acba35288bfcb743ad114d7e.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/7758f1f6acba35288bfcb743ad114d7e.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家亦会带领船员亲自进行战斗，这既包括在海战中陷入接舷战，也包括在各个大陆上的副本战，都将带来同样出众的激烈体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/0396425defc9e0213699b04a1bacc4f5.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/0396425defc9e0213699b04a1bacc4f5.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/0396425defc9e0213699b04a1bacc4f5.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陆上副本中也会充满惊喜，众多强力BOSS和宝物在等着你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/ef2910c676f156ec2274ca7b5277c43c.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/ef2910c676f156ec2274ca7b5277c43c.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/ef2910c676f156ec2274ca7b5277c43c.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑商赚钱，是航海旅行的重要乐趣，而在《航海日记2》中各地的商品价格将根据真实的物品供需关系动态变化，玩家必须随时关注商品动态，及时买入卖出才能赚得收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/de4d1e77730063ea51631b1fc9cb4cdc.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/de4d1e77730063ea51631b1fc9cb4cdc.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/de4d1e77730063ea51631b1fc9cb4cdc.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >舰船不只是玩家征服远方的工具，也是承载玩家梦想的家园，玩家可以带领船员在船上展开种植、养殖与锻造等各种活动，不但可以获得丰富的收益，还能让这个小家变得更加温馨！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a7a9b48ad8a334f7f0f1985df153289c.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a7a9b48ad8a334f7f0f1985df153289c.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/a7a9b48ad8a334f7f0f1985df153289c.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/33bb2ccb973c475a25708a8857ea2622.avif?t=1728732179\" width=615 height=100 /></span>《航海日记2》以真实世界为基础，搭建了一个极为庞大的开放世界，其拥有真实的陆地、海洋地形，连坐标与洋流系统也都是真实的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/30dc3fe406b1dd67e5832c78d0c6301a.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/30dc3fe406b1dd67e5832c78d0c6301a.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/30dc3fe406b1dd67e5832c78d0c6301a.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时在这个开放世界中充满了令人赞叹的细节，本作目前已开放包含200多个可探索的城市，并通过精致的像素画风将每一个城市都描绘的活灵活现、别具一格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/20b3361fed3d21524310075012e6442c.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/20b3361fed3d21524310075012e6442c.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/20b3361fed3d21524310075012e6442c.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在中国的天津卫，你可以在街头看到说书的与耍猴的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/12ed88380f0ad813e13b68d60c3b3888.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/12ed88380f0ad813e13b68d60c3b3888.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/12ed88380f0ad813e13b68d60c3b3888.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在日本你可以看到樱花与鸟居。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/5ea9438eee2ed4dabccb5e389ae7ea76.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/5ea9438eee2ed4dabccb5e389ae7ea76.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/5ea9438eee2ed4dabccb5e389ae7ea76.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在越南你可以看到金灿灿的东南亚庙宇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/31ec57cfdafb574e46bcb99c9662ef22.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/31ec57cfdafb574e46bcb99c9662ef22.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/31ec57cfdafb574e46bcb99c9662ef22.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在欧洲则可以看到壮观的教堂与古堡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2624544b13b3478134c0d4bf962e5beb.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2624544b13b3478134c0d4bf962e5beb.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2624544b13b3478134c0d4bf962e5beb.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/2935fcb817ba87ccbf1ca1c3caff4d3a.avif?t=1728732179\" width=615 height=100 /></span>《航海日记2》中你并不是唯一的冒险者，还有无数玩家的舰队在与你同行，有时你们会互相竞争，抢夺宝物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/3257648fcee76f9ca74bab6e7d5dff88.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/3257648fcee76f9ca74bab6e7d5dff88.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/3257648fcee76f9ca74bab6e7d5dff88.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时你们也会互相合作，组成强大的联合舰队，去挑战那些一个人难以战胜的敌人，比如海盗的老巢，又或者深海中的巨怪等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/e0403e3bcdf44b5c0586f942360c087b.poster.avif?t=1728732179\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/e0403e3bcdf44b5c0586f942360c087b.webm?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202430/extras/e0403e3bcdf44b5c0586f942360c087b.mp4?t=1728732179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，《航海日记2》在体验上其实颇有老《大航海时代》的感觉，看似小巧，实则内容极为丰富！每一个部分都极具深度与乐趣，一定能带给你一段丰富多彩又荡气回肠的海上冒险！</p>",
